### User Auth - Onboarding Admin APIs
### Required scope: SCOPE_TENANT_CREATE_APPROVE

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@adminAccessToken = 01d2a4fc-0362-4af3-ac57-95e393bb45c9
@applicationId = c97ac6a1-fb66-4f82-b466-7fa6759b9668

### 1) List applications (all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/applications
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

### 2) List applications (filtered by type)
GET {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/applications?type=BRAND
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

### 3) Approve application
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/applications/{{applicationId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

### 4) Reject application
POST {{baseUrl}}/onboarding/applications/{{applicationId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reason": "invalid evidence"
}
